  <description><![CDATA[<p>Located on the main street in Sauze d'Oulx, the family-run Serendipity has been completely refurbished to a high standard using timber and quality materials. The Serendipity's new décor combines rustic, mountain style with modren elegance. With great staff and comfortable rooms, the Serendipity is known for its welcoming atmosphere alongside the stunning interior of the individually designed rooms. This small hotel is setting a new benchmark for 3 star hotels in Sauze d'Oulx. <strong>This hotel is bookable on request only. Please call our reservations team to enquire.</strong></p>]]></description>
